ed\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2369:\"<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" width=\"550\"><p>Don&#39;t know if this will ever sink in. What an amazing night. Thankful to celebrate with the fans in LA.</p>\n<p>&mdash; Clayton Kershaw (@ClaytonKersh22) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ClaytonKersh22/status/479511080993951744\">June 19, 2014</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>Last night I had to opportunity to be at the Dodgers game for Clayton Kershaw&#8217;s first no hitter. What an honor and a blessing that was.</p>\n<p>Here are some of the highlights from the night.</p>\n<h3>Scully calls Kershaw&#8217;s no-no <ins datetime=\"2014-06-18\">06/18/14</ins> | 00:07:25</h3>\n<p><iframe src=\"http://m.dodgers.mlb.com/shared/video/embed/embed.html?content_id=33848827&topic_id=8878826&width=650&height=424&property=mlb\" width=\"650\" height=\"424\" frameborder=\"0\">Your browser does not support iframes.</iframe></p>\n<h3>My Surprise</h3>\n<p><iframe width=\"1152\" height=\"648\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/AeDr0rG_GBM?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<h3>The Dodgers GIFs</h3>\n<p><div class=\"column-grid column-grid-5\"><div class=\"column column-span-1 column-push-0 column-first\"><p>\n<img alt=\"The Final Strikeout\" src=\"https://31.media.tumblr.com/3b70631c931df4d66cde8d0914331d90/tumblr_n7ehv3FOQq1ro5xweo3_250.gif\"></p>\n</div><br />\n<div class=\"column column-span-1 column-push-0\"><p>\n<img alt=\"Ellen is re-leaved\" src=\"https://38.media.tumblr.com/736ebaa08f8f339fe8b4f50985a24645/tumblr_n7ehv3FOQq1ro5xweo1_250.gif\" ></p>\n</div><br />\n<div class=\"column column-span-1 column-push-0\"><p>\n<img alt=\"Jumping on Kershaw\" src=\"https://38.media.tumblr.com/1886534f969230ea3248ef1a08d0bfc2/tumblr_n7ehv3FOQq1ro5xweo2_400.gif\"></p>\n</div><br />\n<div class=\"column column-span-1 column-push-0\"><p>\n<img alt=\"Yeah! The NoNo ball\" src=\"https://38.media.tumblr.com/f4369c0eb04483db304adb7dd73b3940/tumblr_n7ehv3FOQq1ro5xweo4_400.gif\"></p>\n</div><br />\n<div class=\"column column-span-1 column-push-0 column-last\"><p>\n<img alt=\"Dodgers bubble dance party\" src=\"https://37.media.tumblr.com/7f94a63cc004f463ac6a814ab622182e/tumblr_n7ehv3FOQq1ro5xweo5_r1_400.gif\"></p>\n</div></div></p>\n<p><br style=\"clear:both\"><br />\nCongrats!</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/AustinPassy/~4/7n2KggRvGLA\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"http://austin.passy.co/2014/clayton-kershaw-no-hitter/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"http://austin.passy.co/2014/clayton-kershaw-no-hitter/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"LED Filament Bulbs\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/AustinPassy/~3/u8RiKL9P2ts/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";