 Login 2 <a href=\"https://plugins.trac.wordpress.org/changeset/698248/custom-login\" title=\"Version 2.0 released April, 16th 2013\" target=\"_blank\">was released</a> we added the ability to extend how that plugin functioned. Since version 2 was released in April of 2013 we&#8217;ve added 6 extensions, with more on the way.</p>\n<h3>Extensions Currently Available</h3>\n<p><big><strong><a title=\"Custom Login Bundle\" href=\"http://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-bundle/\">The Bundle</a></strong>; All extensions for a steal!</big></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Custom Login: <a title=\"Custom Login Stealth Login\" href=\"http://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-stealth-login/\">Stealth Login</a> â€“ obscure your login URL.</li>\n<li>Custom Login: <a title=\"Custom Login Page Template\" href=\"http://frosty.media/plugins/plugin/custom-login-page-template/\">Page Template</a> â€“ turn a WordPress page into a login form.</li>\n<li>Custom Login: <a title=\"WordPress Login Redirects\" href=\"http://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-redirects/\">Redirects</a> â€“ redirect users by role after logging in.</li>\n<li>Custom Login: <a title=\"Custom Login No Password Logins\" href=\"http://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-no-password-login/\">No Password</a> â€“ allow users to login without a password.</li>\n<li>Custom Login: <a href=\"http://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/\" title=\"Style Pack #1\">Style Pack #1</a> &#8211; four custom login styles that can be activated at the push of a button.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>In Development/Ideas</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><del datetime=\"2014-10-05T00:17:45+00:00\">User Hash Key logins (think generated guest logins with-out having to use the login form).</del></li>\n<li>Email Logins for usernames.</li>\n<li>2-step Authentication.</li>\n<li><del datetime=\"2014-01-28T00:17:45+00:00\">Custom Login page</del></li>\n<li>â€œSuper Userâ€ only access for client sites.</li>\n<li><del datetime=\"2015-01-07T00:17:45+00:00\">WordPress Login CSS style remover (for sites that see a quick flash of the default login page)</del> &#8211; option added in Version 3.0 of Custom Login.</li>\n<li>Submit button styles!</li>\n<li>Custom Login Templates</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>Quick FAQ&#8217;s</h5>\n<p class=\"alert\">Grant access to Custom Login and be sure you turn on the CSS output of the plugin by visiting the Settings <strong>></strong> <em>General Settings</em> tab and checking <em>Activate</em>.</p>\n<p><strong>For those looking to showoff your login screen, check out the <a href=\"http://flickr.com/groups/custom-login/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Flickr group</a>! Share you designs with the community!</strong></p>\n<h4>GitHub</h4>\n<iframe src=\"https://frosty.media?github-btn=true&user=thefrosty&repo=custom-login&type=watch&count=true&size=large\" allowtransparency=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"0\" width=\"115\" height=\"30\" name=\"gform_github-button\"></iframe>\n<p>Follow development on <a href=\"https://github.com/thefrosty/custom-login/\" title=\"Custom Login on GitHub\" target=\"_blank\">GitHub</a>, submit issues, fork your own version or help make Custom Login better.</p>\n<h3>Screenshots</h3>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/custom-login-3-design-settings/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/custom-login-3-design-settings-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail\" alt=\"Custom Login 3 Design Settings\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/custom-login-3-general-settings/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/custom-login-3-general-settings-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail\" alt=\"Custom Login 3 General Settings\" /></a>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/\">Custom Login 3.0</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media\">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:47:\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"No Password Login\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-no-password-login/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-no-password-login/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 06 Oct 2014 03:35:32 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:43:\"http://frosty.media/?post_type=plugin&p=129\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:326:\"<p>Login Without Password in WordPress? Now you can with this Custom Login extension: No Password Login WordPress. </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-no-password-login/\">No Password Login</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media\">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Austin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1815:\"<p class=\"alert\">This plugin is an extension and requires <a href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/\" title=\"Custom Login\">Custom Login</a> (version <strong>3.x</strong>) which can be downloaded for free <a href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/\">here</a>.</p><p>Allow users to login without having to remember their password. This plugin is safe and secure and uses WordPress&#8217; best coding practices.</p>\n<p>With a simple shortcode you can allow a form where a user can enter their email or username which then sends them an email with a login URL key. That URL can only be used once and expires after 10 min.</p>\n<h3>An example</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/custom-login-no-password-login.gif\" alt=\"Custom Login No Password Login animation\" width=\"1190\" height=\"765\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-16624\" /></p>\n<h3>Screenshots</h3>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-no-password-login/custom-login-no-password-settings/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/custom-login-no-password-settings-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail\" alt=\"Custom Login No Password settings\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-no-password-login/custom-login-no-password-login-2/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/custom-login-no-password-login-150x150.gif\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail\" alt=\"Custom Login No Password Login animation\" /></a>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-no-password-login/\">No Password Login</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media\">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-no-password-login/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Login Redirects\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-redirects/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-redirects/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 25 Apr 2014 03:31:33 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:43:\"http://frosty.media/?post_type=plugin&p=125\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:325:\"<p>Manage user roles and redirect said user after successful logins with this Custom Login Redirect extension for WordPress.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-redirects/\">Login Redirects</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media\">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Austin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3096:\"<p class=\"alert\">This plugin is an extension and requires <a href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/\" title=\"Custom Login\">Custom Login</a> (version <strong>3.x</strong>) which can be downloaded for free <a href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/\">here</a>.</p><p>When it comes to managing a WordPress site which allows signups, you rarely want subscriber roles to view the dashboard or admin pages after they log in.</p>\n<h3>WordPress solutions</h3>\n<p>WordPress has many hooks and filters which allow you to control visibility access on a user role base. But this method requires you to understand PHP.</p>\n<p>So, hereâ€™s an easy way to redirect subscribers users (or which ever role you&#8217;d like) to a default WordPress page or custom URL (of your choosing) after said user logs in.</p>\n<h3>How to use it</h3>\n<p>There is really only four options needed for this plugin, and three of those have default values. </p>\n<ol>\n<li>On/Off</li>\n<li><del datetime=\"2014-11-04T00:53:21+00:00\">Redirect minimum user role.</del> <ins datetime=\"2014-11-04T00:53:21+00:00\">Removed in 1.1.0</ins></li>\n<li>Redirect To (A WordPress page).</li>\n<li>Redirect URL (when Redirect to equals &#8220;A Custom URL&#8221;) <em>local URLs only</em>.</li>\n<li>Redirect to URL for each registered role (if empty uses the <em>Redirect URL</em> setting).</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Manage user roles and redirect said user after successful logins with this Custom Login Redirect extension for WordPress.</p>\n<h3>Screenshots</h3>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-redirects/custom-login-redirects-settings/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/custom-login-redirects-settings-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail\" alt=\"Custom Login Redirects settings page\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-redirects/custom-login-redirects-custom-url/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/custom-login-redirects-custom-url-150x150.gif\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail\" alt=\"Custom Login Redirects custom URL redirect animation\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-redirects/custom-login-redirects-wp-page/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/custom-login-redirects-wp-page-150x150.gif\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail\" alt=\"Custom Login Redirects WordPress page URL redirect animation\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-redirects/custom-login-redirects-user-roles/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/custom-login-redirects-user-roles-150x150.gif\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail\" alt=\"Custom Login Redirects redirect URL by user role animation\" /></a>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-redirects/\">Login Redirects</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media\">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-redirects/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Page Template\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-page-template/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-page-template/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 29 Jan 2014 04:24:13 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:43:\"http://frosty.media/?post_type=plugin&p=121\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:343:\"<p>The Custom Login Page Template is an extension for the Custom Login WordPress plugin allowing login forms to be generated on any WP page.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-page-template/\">Page Template</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media\">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Austin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2569:\"<p class=\"alert\">This plugin is an extension and requires <a href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/\" title=\"Custom Login\">Custom Login</a> (version <strong>3.x</strong>) which can be downloaded for free <a href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/\">here</a>.</p><p>Create your own WordPress Custom Login page from any page you previously created in WordPress.</p>\n<p class=\"alert\">You must <a href=\"http://codex.wordpress.org/Codex:Creating_a_New_Page\" target=\"_blank\">create</a> a new blank WordPress page or use an existing one. Note: the content will be replaced with the login form.</p>\n<h3>How to use it</h3>\n<p>There is only two options in this plugin, and one turns it on and off.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>On/Off</li>\n<li>Your custom login page.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>That&#8217;s it! Once setup the WordPress login form will replace the default content on the page set in the settings.</p>\n<h3>Screenshots</h3>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-page-template/custom-login-page-template-settings/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/custom-login-page-template-settings-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail\" alt=\"Custom Login Page Template settings\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-page-template/custom-login-page-template-setting-enabled/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/custom-login-page-template-setting-enabled-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail\" alt=\"Custom Login Page Template Enabled set to &quot;Sample Page&quot;\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-page-template/custom-login-page-template-login-page/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/custom-login-page-template-login-page-150x150.png\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail\" alt=\"Custom Login Page Template &quot;Sample Page&quot; front end\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-page-template/page-template-login-page/\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/page-template-login-page-150x150.gif\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail\" alt=\"Custom Login Page Template animated walkthrough *with Stealth Login enabled\" /></a>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-page-template/\">Page Template</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://frosty.media\">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a: